| # | Deliverable | Verified |
|---|------------|----------|
| 1 | Core sample rows obtained (SELECT TOP N returned data) | [ ] |
| 2 | Row count obtained | [ ] |
| 3 | Date range / timestamp analysis done (Tier A1) | [ ] |
| 4 | NULL pattern analysis recorded | [ ] |
